-- Certificates --

1. CISCO ISE uses Admin Certificates to secure a connection between admin and ISE. 
2. ISE uses EAP certificates  which is for communication between end points like mobile, laptop. etc. 
3. ISE users Portal ceritificates which is for guest portal, device authentication portal. basically end user portal. 
4. ISE uses wildcard portal which uses * like *.google.com

